name: PDF (Portable Document Format), version 1.5
description: Version of PDF, developed by Adobe Systems Incorporated and described by Adobe as a general document representation language. Represents a fixed page-layout.  Version 1.5 of the PDF format was associated with Acrobat and Adobe Reader 6.0.
